{"version": 2, "width": 110, "height": 42, "timestamp": 1784845304, "command": "pi --help", "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/zsh", "TERM": "dumb"}}
[2.399394, "o", "\nMeta Launcher Options:\n  --internet                          Enable internet access (macOS only)\n  --dangerously-enable-internet-mode  Enable internet access without sandboxing (macOS/Linux only)\n  --secure-internet-mode              Enable secure internet access without user data (macOS/Linux only)\n  --dangerously-disable-osx-sandbox   Disable the macOS sandbox\n  --add-mcp-tools                     Launch the MCP tools TUI\n  --with-proxy                        Override the Plugboard proxy URL\n  --doctor                            Run diagnostics and auto-fixes (migrated to agent-doctor)\n  --rage                              Collect troubleshooting data (migrated to agent-doctor)\n  --meta-agent-role                   Role for the agent (macOS and Linux only)\n  --startup-context-mode              Activate these context modes on fresh session start, overriding the `[rules.startup_mode]` config and any last-used modes. Comma-separated list of mode names. Subagents ignore this flag; only the main agent's SessionStart applies it\n  --meta-force-enable-features        Force-enable MetaCode feature names. Comma-separated or repeatable\n\nPi at Meta (https://www.npmjs.com/package/@earendil-works/pi-coding-agent)\nUsing AI Gateway (Anthropic upstream)\nsandbox-exec: sandbox_apply: Operation not permitted\n"]
